quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,164,"Pellet hino e ndeer tagugol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e luutondiral jemma e √Īalorma on, e laa…óe dogooje …óee he maaje kaa…ó…óe nafugol yim…ďe …ďen, e ko Allah Jippini to kammu ( ndowgu), he ndiyam, o wurniri …óam leydi ndin …ďaawo maayugol mayri o Saakti he mayri kala daaba, e waylitugol keneeli …óin e duule eltaa…óe …óen hakkunde leydi e kammu, maandeeji wonannde yim…ďe hakkiloo…ďe ."
  2,165,"Hino he yim…ďe …ďee jogitii…ďe ko woori Allah yerodii…ďe, e…ďe nji…ói …ďe wano no Allah yi…óirtee, [ko] …ďen gom…óim…ďe …ďuri sa…ótude giggol (yi…óde) wonande Allah. Hara …ďen too√Īu…ďe annduno tuma …ďe nji'oyta lepte …óen, wonde doole …óen fof ko Allah heeranii, e wonde Allah ko sa…ótu…óo lepte!."
  2,166,"Tuma nde hisnii jokkanoo…ďe …ďen jokkunoo…ďe …ďen, …ďe nji'i lepte …óen, jokkor…óe …óee ta∆īiri …ďe."
  2,167,"Jokkunoo…ďe …ďen (rewnoo…ďe …ďee) mbi'a: "Hara fehre ruttagol no woodannoo men, men pottitora …ďe wano …ďe pottitori men nii". Ko wano nii Allah Hollirta …ďe golleeji ma…ď…ďe …óin; hayrere e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďe ngonaali njaltoo…ďe e yiite ngen."
  2,168,"Heey mo yim…ďe! √Ďaamee yoga he ko woni ka leydi koo, dagii ko laa…ďi, wata on jokku juri=taa…ďe (taa…ďe) seytaane …óin : Pellet, ko o ga√Īo mo'on fee√Īu…óo."
  2,169,"Anndee ko o yamirta on ko bone e paŇčkare, e nde wowloton he Allah ko on anndaa."